dct_title_s: Mexico and internal provinces Prepared from Humboldt's map & other documents
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Shows major roads, mines, areas of Indian habitation, extent of rivers, cities, and military posts. Includes notes, dates, and text. Prime meridians: Washington and London. In left and right margins: Mexico, No. 38.
